```class Solution {
    public int bestClosingTime(String customers) {
        int minPenalty = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        int bestTime = 0;
        int penalty = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < customers.length(); i++) {
            if (customers.charAt(i) == 'N') {
                penalty++;
            } else {
                penalty -= 1;
            }
            if (penalty < minPenalty) {
                minPenalty = penalty;
                bestTime = i + 1;
            }
        }
        return bestTime;
    }
}```
